# PROTOCOL BUFFER
# SFML 2.0
# OPENAL 
# CG 3.0
# DIRECTX SDK (plugin-dx9)
# CGD3D (plugin-dx9)
# CGGL (plugin-ogl)
# GLEW (plugin-ogl)
